{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"df396b24fc","title":"致彭德怀等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9d8562ac93","index":0,"year":1940,"month":12,"day":10,"articleId":"df396b24fc"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji15","name":"毛泽东全集第15卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji15.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji15":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"29b3c9a80a","type":"paragraph","text":"致彭德怀等电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"df396b24fc"},{"id":"0e0baba15b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1940年12月10日）为迎接新的局势，大量准备并培养干部是极其重要的。抗大总不能取消。但由于分校之分散，对各分校之具体领导应责成各地局及最高军事首长负责。完全统一是不可能的。总校应多注意总经验、指导方针、统一材料之编辑、统一各种教法、培养教员、剂干部，以帮助及加强各分校的领导及教育能力。各地任意抽调校干部是不对的，已有另电纠正。总校机构宜小，而苏北局面扩望再分出一个分校的干部，派去苏北。此分校要比山东分校还姜强些，因为苏北局面是很大的局面。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"df396b24fc"}],"page":{"id":"ad56abef64","publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"df396b24fc","start":271,"end":271}}}},"__N_SSG":true}